SELECT
      s.seqid
    , ref.stub
    , s.cn
    , s.nm
    , coalesce(s.dsc, '') as dsc
    , ref.type
    /*, (
        SELECT json_build_object(
          'name', dt.nm,
          'id', dt.seqid,
          'category', dt.ctg,
          'metadata', dt.meta,
          'create_date', dt.record_create_dt
        )
        FROM datahub.datasource_type dt
        WHERE dt.archive_dt IS NULL
          AND dt.seqid = s.datastore_type_seqid
      ) as "type" */
    , s.version
    , s.meta
    , s.est_sz
    , s.est_record_ct
    , s.conn
    , s.update_sched
    , s.last_update_dt
    , s.msg
    , s.record_create_dt
    , ref.queries
    /*, (
        SELECT jsonb_agg(json_build_object(
          'id', q.seqid,
          'name', q.nm,
          'description', coalesce(q.dsc, ''),
          'code', q.code,
          'metadata', q.meta,
          'last_update_date', q.last_update_dt,
          'create_date', q.record_create_dt
        ))
        FROM datahub.query q
        WHERE q.datastore_seqid = s.seqid
          AND q.archive_dt IS NULL
      )::jsonb as queries*/
    , ref.aliases
    /*, (
        SELECT jsonb_agg(json_build_object(
          'profile', json_build_object(
            'name', p.nm,
            'id', p.seqid
          ),
          'alias', json_build_object(
            'name', a.nm,
            'description', coalesce(a.dsc, ''),
            'id', a.seqid
          )
        ))
        FROM datahub.profile p
          LEFT JOIN datahub.alias a ON p.seqid = a.profile_seqid
        WHERE a.datastore_seqid = s.seqid
          AND p.archive_dt IS NULL
          AND a.archive_dt IS NULL
      )::jsonb as aliases*/
    , ref.tags
    /*, coalesce((
        SELECT jsonb_agg(tag.nm)
        FROM datahub.tag
          LEFT JOIN datahub.tag_assc ta ON ta.tag_seqid = tag.seqid
        WHERE ta.datastore_seqid = s.seqid
          AND ta.archive_dt IS NULL
          AND tag.archive_dt IS NULL
      ), '[]'::jsonb)::jsonb as tags*/
    , ref.attributes
    /*, (
        SELECT json_agg(json_build_object(
          'name', ca.nm,
          'value', json_build_object(
            'create_date', cav.record_create_dt,
            'value', coalesce(cav.value, ca.default_value),
            'id', cav.seqid
           )
        ))
        FROM datahub.custom_attribute ca
          LEFT JOIN datahub.custom_attribute_value cav
            ON ca.seqid = cav.custom_attribute_seqid
        WHERE cav.datastore_seqid = s.seqid
          AND ca.archive_dt IS NULL
          AND cav.archive_dt IS NULL
      )::jsonb as attributes*/
    , (
        SELECT jsonb_agg(json_build_object(
          'id', t.seqid,
          'name', json_build_object(
            'logical', coalesce(t.cn, t.nm),
            'physical', t.nm
          ),
          'description', coalesce(t.dsc, ''),
          'estimated_size', t.est_sz,
          'estimated_record_count', t.est_record_ct,
          'item_count', (
            SELECT count(fld.seqid)
            FROM datahub.datafield fld
            WHERE fld.datatable_seqid = t.seqid
              AND fld.archive_dt IS NULL
          ),
          'last_update_date', t.last_update_dt,
          'update_schedule', t.update_sched,
          'aliases', (
            SELECT json_agg(json_build_object(
              'profile', json_build_object(
                'name', p.nm,
                'id', p.seqid
              ),
              'alias', json_build_object(
                'value', a.nm,
                'description', coalesce(a.dsc, ''),
                'id', a.seqid
              )
            ))
            FROM datahub.alias a
              LEFT JOIN datahub.profile p
                ON a.profile_seqid = p.seqid
            WHERE datatable_seqid = t.seqid
          )
        ))
        FROM datahub.datatable t
        WHERE t.datastore_seqid = s.seqid
          AND t.archive_dt IS NULL
      ) as sets
  FROM datahub.datastore s
    LEFT JOIN datahub.vw_data_source_ref ref ON ref.id = s.seqid
  WHERE s.archive_dt IS NULL;
;

SELECT cc.seqid,
    cc.source,
    cc.source_seqid,
    cc.db_user,
    cc.blame,
    cc.change,
    cc.record_create_dt,
        CASE
            WHEN ((string_to_array(cc.source, '.'::text))[2] = 'datastore'::text) THEN 'source'::text
            WHEN ((string_to_array(cc.source, '.'::text))[2] = 'datatable'::text) THEN 'set'::text
            WHEN ((string_to_array(cc.source, '.'::text))[2] = 'datafield'::text) THEN 'item'::text
            WHEN ((string_to_array(cc.source, '.'::text))[2] = 'query'::text) THEN 'query'::text
            WHEN ((string_to_array(cc.source, '.'::text))[2] = 'alias'::text) THEN 'alias'::text
            WHEN ((string_to_array(cc.source, '.'::text))[2] = 'custom_attribute_value'::text) THEN 'attribute'::text
            WHEN ((string_to_array(cc.source, '.'::text))[2] = 'datafield_compliance_type'::text) THEN 'policy'::text
            ELSE NULL::text
        END AS type,
        CASE
            WHEN ((cc.change ->> 'op'::text) = 'DELETE'::text) THEN NULL::jsonb
            WHEN ((string_to_array(cc.source, '.'::text))[2] = 'datastore'::text) THEN jsonb_build_object('source', cc.source_seqid, 'set', NULL::unknown, 'item', NULL::unknown, 'query', NULL::unknown)
            WHEN ((string_to_array(cc.source, '.'::text))[2] = 'datatable'::text) THEN ( SELECT jsonb_build_object('source', d1.datastore_seqid, 'set', d1.seqid, 'item', NULL::unknown, 'query', NULL::unknown) AS jsonb_build_object
               FROM datahub.datatable d1
              WHERE (d1.seqid = cc.source_seqid))
            WHEN ((string_to_array(cc.source, '.'::text))[2] = 'datafield'::text) THEN ( SELECT jsonb_build_object('source', d3.datastore_seqid, 'set', d2.datatable_seqid, 'item', cc.source_seqid, 'query', NULL::unknown) AS jsonb_build_object
               FROM (datahub.datafield d2
                 LEFT JOIN datahub.datatable d3 ON ((d3.seqid = d2.datatable_seqid)))
              WHERE (d2.seqid = cc.source_seqid))
            WHEN ((string_to_array(cc.source, '.'::text))[2] = 'query'::text) THEN ( SELECT jsonb_build_object('source', q.datastore_seqid, 'set', NULL::unknown, 'item', NULL::unknown, 'query', q.seqid) AS jsonb_build_object
               FROM datahub.query q
              WHERE (q.seqid = cc.source_seqid))
            WHEN ((string_to_array(cc.source, '.'::text))[2] = 'alias'::text) THEN ( SELECT jsonb_build_object('source', t.source_id, 'set', t.set_id, 'item', t.item_id, 'query', NULL::unknown) AS jsonb_build_object
               FROM datahub.vw_thesaurus t
              WHERE (t.alias_id = cc.source_seqid))
            WHEN ((string_to_array(cc.source, '.'::text))[2] = 'custom_attribute_value'::text) THEN ( SELECT jsonb_build_object('source',
                    CASE
                        WHEN (cav.datastore_seqid IS NOT NULL) THEN cav.datastore_seqid
                        WHEN (cav.datatable_seqid IS NOT NULL) THEN cdt.datastore_seqid
                        WHEN (cav.datafield_seqid IS NOT NULL) THEN ( SELECT tt.datastore_seqid
                           FROM datahub.datatable tt
                          WHERE (tt.seqid = cdf.datatable_seqid))
                        ELSE NULL::text
                    END, 'set',
                    CASE
                        WHEN (cav.datatable_seqid IS NOT NULL) THEN cav.datatable_seqid
                        WHEN (cav.datafield_seqid IS NOT NULL) THEN cdf.datatable_seqid
                        ELSE NULL::text
                    END, 'item', cav.datafield_seqid, 'query', NULL::unknown) AS jsonb_build_object
               FROM (((datahub.custom_attribute_value cav
                 LEFT JOIN datahub.datastore cds ON ((cds.seqid = cav.datastore_seqid)))
                 LEFT JOIN datahub.datatable cdt ON ((cdt.seqid = cav.datatable_seqid)))
                 LEFT JOIN datahub.datafield cdf ON ((cdf.seqid = cav.datafield_seqid)))
              WHERE (cav.seqid = cc.source_seqid))
            WHEN ((string_to_array(cc.source, '.'::text))[2] = 'datafield_compliance_type'::text) THEN ( SELECT jsonb_build_object('source', t2.datastore_seqid, 'set', t2.seqid, 'item', f.seqid, 'query', NULL::unknown) AS jsonb_build_object
               FROM ((datahub.datafield_compliance_type dct
                 LEFT JOIN datahub.datafield f ON ((f.seqid = dct.datafield_seqid)))
                 LEFT JOIN datahub.datatable t2 ON ((f.datatable_seqid = t2.seqid)))
              WHERE (dct.compliance_type_seqid = cc.source_seqid))
            ELSE NULL::jsonb
        END AS reference,
    EXTRACT(day FROM (max(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP) - min(cc.record_create_dt))) AS age
   FROM datahub.catalog_changelog cc
  GROUP BY cc.seqid, cc.source, cc.source_seqid, cc.db_user, cc.blame, cc.change, cc.record_create_dt;

                   FROM ( SELECT jsonb_array_elements(( SELECT (COALESCE(jsonb_agg(jsonb_build_object('id', rur.seqid, 'name', rur.nm, 'description', COALESCE(rur.dsc, ''::text), 'protected', rur.protected, 'assignment', json_build_object('id', rura.seqid, 'create_date', rura.record_create_dt, 'inherited', false, 'inherited_from', '[]'::jsonb), 'metadata', rur.meta, 'create_date', rur.record_create_dt, 'inherited', false)), '[]'::jsonb) || COALESCE(( SELECT jsonb_agg(jsonb_build_object('id', rur2.seqid, 'name', rur2.nm, 'description', COALESCE(rur2.dsc, ''::text), 'protected', rur2.protected, 'assignment', json_build_object('id', rura2.seqid, 'create_date', rura2.record_create_dt, 'inherited', true, 'inherited_from', ( SELECT jsonb_agg(ug3.nm) AS jsonb_agg

 CASE

 END))), '[]'::jsonb) || COALESCE(( SELECT jsonb_agg(jsonb_build_object('id', p2_1.seqid, 'name', p2_1.nm, 'description', COALESCE(p2_1.dsc, ''::text), 'create_date', p2_1.record_create_dt, 'assignment', jsonb_build_object('id', up2.seqid, 'create_date', up2.record_create_dt, 'inherited',

   CASE
    WHEN (xup.login_seqid IS NOT NULL) THEN false

        LEFT JOIN datahub.user_role ur4 ON ((ur4.seqid = xura2.user_role_seqid)))
     WHERE (xp2.seqid = xp.seqid))))) AS jsonb_agg
    FROM (((datahub.group_member xgm
      LEFT JOIN datahub.user_role_assignment xura ON ((xura.user_group_seqid = xgm.user_group_seqid)))
      LEFT JOIN datahub.user_profile xup ON ((xup.user_role_seqid = xura.user_role_seqid)))
      LEFT JOIN datahub.profile xp ON ((xp.seqid = xup.profile_seqid)))
   WHERE (xgm.login_seqid = l.seqid)), '[]'::jsonb)) || COALESCE(( SELECT jsonb_agg(jsonb_build_object('id', p3_1.seqid, 'name', p3_1.nm, 'description', COALESCE(p3_1.dsc, ''::text), 'create_date', p3_1.record_create_dt, 'assignment', jsonb_build_object('id', up3.seqid, 'create_date', up3.record_create_dt, 'inherited',

    COALESCE(login.enabled, (COALESCE(login.expire_dt, (CURRENT_TIMESTAMP - '00:01:00'::interval)) < CURRENT_TIMESTAMP)) AS enabled,
    (COALESCE(login.expire_dt, (CURRENT_TIMESTAMP - '00:01:00'::interval)) > CURRENT_TIMESTAMP) AS expired,
    login.expire_dt AS expiration_date
   FROM (( SELECT jsonb_build_object('roles', ( SELECT COALESCE(json_agg(jsonb_build_object('id', base.id, 'name', base.name)), '[]'::json) AS "coalesce"
                   FROM ( SELECT vr.id,
                            vr.name
                           FROM (datahub.ldap_map m
                             LEFT JOIN datahub.vw_user_role vr ON ((vr.id = m.role_seqid)))
                          WHERE ((m.dn = lm.dn) AND (m.role_seqid IS NOT NULL))
                        UNION
                         SELECT ur.seqid AS id,
                            ur.nm AS name
                           FROM ((datahub.login l
                             LEFT JOIN datahub.user_role_assignment ura ON ((ura.login_seqid = l.seqid)))
                             LEFT JOIN datahub.user_role ur ON ((ura.user_role_seqid = ur.seqid)))
                          WHERE (l.ldap_id = lm.dn)) base
                  WHERE (base.id IS NOT NULL)), 'groups', ( SELECT COALESCE(json_agg(jsonb_build_object('id', gbase.id, 'name', gbase.name)), '[]'::json) AS "coalesce"
                   FROM ( SELECT vg.id,
                            vg.name
                           FROM (datahub.ldap_map m
                             LEFT JOIN datahub.vw_user_group vg ON ((vg.id = m.role_seqid)))
                          WHERE ((m.dn = lm.dn) AND (m.group_seqid IS NOT NULL))
                        UNION
                         SELECT ug.seqid AS id,
                            ug.nm AS name
                           FROM ((datahub.login l
                             LEFT JOIN datahub.group_member gm ON ((gm.login_seqid = l.seqid)))
                             LEFT JOIN datahub.user_group ug ON ((gm.user_group_seqid = ug.seqid)))
                          WHERE (l.ldap_id = lm.dn)) gbase
                  WHERE (gbase.id IS NOT NULL)), 'profiles', ( SELECT COALESCE(json_agg(jsonb_build_object('id', pbase.id, 'name', pbase.name)), '[]'::json) AS "coalesce"
                   FROM ( SELECT p.seqid AS id,
                            p.nm AS name
                           FROM (datahub.ldap_map m
                             LEFT JOIN datahub.profile p ON ((p.seqid = m.profile_seqid)))
                          WHERE ((m.dn = 'cn=admin,ou=roles,dc=example,dc=com'::text) AND (m.profile_seqid IS NOT NULL))
                        UNION
                         SELECT p2.seqid AS id,
                            p2.nm AS name
                           FROM ((datahub.login l
                             LEFT JOIN datahub.user_profile up ON ((up.login_seqid = l.seqid)))
                             LEFT JOIN datahub.profile p2 ON ((up.profile_seqid = p2.seqid)))
                          WHERE ((l.ldap_id = lm.dn) AND (p2.archive_dt IS NULL))) pbase
                  WHERE (pbase.id IS NOT NULL)), 'rights', ( SELECT COALESCE(json_agg(jsonb_build_object('id', ra.right_seqid, 'resource', sr.nm, 'name',
                        CASE
                            WHEN (ra.force = 'd'::bpchar) THEN ('deny:'::text || srr.nm)
                            WHEN (ra.force = 'a'::bpchar) THEN ('allow:'::text || srr.nm)
                            ELSE srr.nm
                        END)), '[]'::json) AS "coalesce"
                   FROM (((datahub.right_assign ra
                     LEFT JOIN datahub.system_resource_right srr ON ((srr.seqid = ra.right_seqid)))
                     LEFT JOIN datahub.system_resource sr ON ((sr.seqid = srr.system_resource_seqid)))
                     LEFT JOIN datahub.login l ON ((ra.login_seqid = l.seqid)))
                  WHERE ((l.seqid = ra.login_seqid) AND (l.ldap_id = lm.dn)))) AS meta,
            lm.dn
           FROM datahub.ldap_map lm) tmp
     LEFT JOIN datahub.login ON ((login.ldap_id = tmp.dn)))
  WHERE (((tmp.meta -> 'roles'::text) IS NOT NULL) AND ((tmp.meta -> 'roles'::text) <> 'null'::jsonb) AND ((tmp.meta -> 'groups'::text) IS NOT NULL) AND ((tmp.meta -> 'groups'::text) <> 'null'::jsonb));

SELECT p.seqid AS id,
    p.eml AS email,
    p.login_seqid AS login_id,
    l.username,
    l.ldap_id AS ldap,
    jsonb_build_object('id', p.seqid, 'firstname', p.gn, 'lastname', p.sn, 'display', COALESCE(p.dn, NULLIF(TRIM(BOTH FROM ((p.gn || ' '::text) || p.sn)), ''::text), l.username), 'title', p.title, 'email', p.eml, 'phone', p.phone, 'enabled',
        CASE
            WHEN (p.archive_dt IS NOT NULL) THEN false
            WHEN (l.enabled = false) THEN false
            WHEN (l.expire_dt < timezone('UTC'::text, now())) THEN false
            ELSE p.enabled
        END, 'image_href', p.avatar_url, 'metadata', p.meta, 'username', l.username, 'login_id', l.seqid) AS data,
    l.archive_dt AS login_archive_dt,
    p.archive_dt AS person_archive_dt
   FROM (datahub.person p
     LEFT JOIN datahub.login l ON ((l.seqid = p.login_seqid)));

SELECT p.seqid AS person_id,
    l.seqid AS login_id,
    l.ldap_id,
    l.username,
    jsonb_build_object('stewardships', ( SELECT jsonb_agg(DISTINCT jsonb_build_object('source', jsonb_build_object('id', s.datastore_seqid, 'name', jsonb_build_object('physical', ds.nm, 'logical', COALESCE(ds.cn, ds.nm))), 'role', s.role, 'create_date', s.record_create_dt)) AS jsonb_agg
           FROM (datahub.datastore_person s
             LEFT JOIN datahub.datastore ds ON ((ds.seqid = s.datastore_seqid)))
          WHERE ((s.archive_dt IS NULL) AND (ds.archive_dt IS NULL))), 'tickets', ( SELECT jsonb_agg(DISTINCT jsonb_build_object('id', t.seqid, 'creator', (t.creator_seqid = p.seqid), 'assignee', (t.assignee_seqid = p.seqid), 'participant', true, 'summary', t.summary)) AS jsonb_agg
           FROM datahub.ticket t
          WHERE ((t.archive_dt IS NULL) AND ((t.creator_seqid = p.seqid) OR (t.assignee_seqid = p.seqid) OR (t.seqid IN ( SELECT ta.ticket_seqid
                   FROM datahub.ticket_activity ta
                  WHERE ((ta.creator_seqid = p.seqid) AND (ta.archive_dt IS NULL))))))), 'ticket_agencies', ( SELECT jsonb_agg(DISTINCT jsonb_build_object('id', tt.seqid, 'name', tt.nm, 'description', COALESCE(tt.dsc, ''::text))) AS jsonb_agg
           FROM (datahub.ticket_type_agent tta
             LEFT JOIN datahub.ticket_type tt ON ((tt.seqid = tta.ticket_type_seqid)))
          WHERE ((tta.archive_dt IS NULL) AND (tta.person_seqid = p.seqid))), 'changelog', ( SELECT jsonb_agg(DISTINCT jsonb_build_object('id', h.seqid, 'change', h.change, 'date', h.record_create_dt, 'type', h.type, 'reference', h.reference)) AS jsonb_agg
           FROM datahub.vw_history h
          WHERE (h.blame = l.username))) AS impact
   FROM (datahub.person p
     LEFT JOIN datahub.login l ON ((p.login_seqid = l.seqid)));

SELECT sys.seqid AS id,
    sys.nm AS name,
    COALESCE(sys.dsc, ''::text) AS description,
    ( SELECT jsonb_agg(y.x) AS jsonb_agg
           FROM ( SELECT jsonb_build_object('id', s.seqid, 'code', ( SELECT jsonb_build_object('id', sc.cd, 'description', COALESCE(sc.dsc, ''::text), 'label', sc.label, 'is_problem', sc.problem, 'warning', sc.warning, 'color', sc.color) AS jsonb_build_object
                           FROM datahub.status_cd sc
                          WHERE (sc.cd = s.cd)), 'label', s.label, 'message', s.msg, 'create_date', s.record_create_dt) AS x
                   FROM datahub.status s
                  WHERE ((s.system_seqid = sys.seqid) AND (s.archive_dt IS NULL))
                  GROUP BY s.seqid, s.record_create_dt
                  ORDER BY s.record_create_dt DESC) y) AS status,
    ( SELECT p.data
           FROM (datahub.vw_person p
             LEFT JOIN datahub.login l ON ((l.seqid = p.login_id)))
          WHERE (p.id = sys.person_seqid)) AS admin,
    sys.cmd AS command,
    sys.cron_sched AS schedule,
    sys.enabled,
    sys.expire_dt AS expiration_date,
    sys.record_create_dt AS create_date,
    sys.manual
   FROM datahub.system sys
  WHERE (sys.archive_dt IS NULL);

SELECT tag.seqid AS id,
    tag.nm AS name,
    jsonb_build_object('id', tag.seqid, 'name', tag.nm, 'description', COALESCE(tag.dsc, ''::text), 'color', COALESCE(tag.color, 'default'::text), 'create_date', tag.record_create_dt) AS data
   FROM datahub.tag

SELECT t.seqid AS id,
    t.draft,
    t.summary,
    t.last_update_dt AS last_update_date,
    t.due_dt AS due_date,
        CASE
            WHEN (t.resolution_ticket_activity_seqid IS NULL) THEN NULL::timestamp with time zone
            ELSE t.resolution_dt
        END AS resolution_date,
    t.time_estimate_min AS estimated_time,
    t.time_actual_min AS actual_time,
    t.public,
    t.meta AS metadata,
    t.record_create_dt AS create_date,
    pc.data AS creator,
        CASE
            WHEN (pa.id IS NULL) THEN NULL::jsonb
            ELSE pa.data
        END AS assignee,
        CASE
            WHEN (pa.id IS NULL) THEN NULL::jsonb
            ELSE pab.data
        END AS assigned_by,
    json_build_object('id', s.seqid, 'name', s.nm, 'description', COALESCE(s.dsc, ''::text), 'closed', s.closed) AS status,
    jsonb_build_object('id', sla.seqid, 'name', sla.nm, 'sla', sla.sla, 'days_remaining', jsonb_build_object('working', ( SELECT
                CASE
                    WHEN (sla.seqid = 'NONE'::text) THEN NULL::integer
                    ELSE datahub."getRemainingSlaDays"(t.record_create_dt, (sla.sla)::integer)
                END AS "getRemainingSlaDays"), 'calendar',
        CASE
            WHEN (sla.seqid <> 'NONE'::text) THEN date_part('day'::text, ((t.record_create_dt + ('1 day'::interval * ((sla.sla - 1))::double precision)) - CURRENT_TIMESTAMP))
            ELSE NULL::double precision
        END)) AS sla,
    jsonb_build_object('id', tp.seqid, 'name', tp.nm, 'description', COALESCE(tp.dsc, ''::text)) AS type,
    ( SELECT vw_linked_data.data
           FROM datahub.vw_linked_data
          WHERE (vw_linked_data.ticket_id = t.seqid)) AS linked_data,
    ( SELECT jsonb_agg(cmeta.meta) AS jsonb_agg
           FROM ( SELECT jsonb_array_elements(jsonb_agg(((((row_to_json(cta.*))::jsonb - 'search'::text) - 'summary'::text) - 'ticket_id'::text))) AS meta
                   FROM datahub.vw_ticket_activity cta
                  GROUP BY cta.ticket_id, cta.create_date
                 HAVING (cta.ticket_id = t.seqid)
                  ORDER BY cta.create_date) cmeta) AS comments,
    ( SELECT jsonb_agg(jsonb_build_object('person', ( SELECT psub.data
                   FROM datahub.vw_person psub
                  WHERE (psub.id = ts.person_seqid)), 'create_date', ts.record_create_dt)) AS jsonb_agg
           FROM datahub.ticket_subscriber ts
          WHERE (ts.ticket_seqid = t.seqid)) AS subscribers,
    (t.search || to_tsvector('english'::regconfig, COALESCE(TRIM(BOTH FROM array_to_string(( SELECT array_agg(DISTINCT tl.nm) AS array_agg
           FROM (datahub.ticket_label tl
             LEFT JOIN datahub.ticket_label_assc tla ON ((tla.ticket_label_seqid = tl.seqid)))
          WHERE (tla.ticket_seqid = t.seqid)), ' '::text)), ''::text))) AS search,
    NULL::double precision AS sla_days_remaining,
        CASE
            WHEN (t.resolution_ticket_activity_seqid IS NULL) THEN false
            ELSE true
        END AS is_resolved
   FROM ((((((datahub.ticket t
     LEFT JOIN datahub.vw_person pc ON ((pc.id = t.creator_seqid)))
     LEFT JOIN datahub.vw_person pa ON ((pa.id = t.assignee_seqid)))
     LEFT JOIN datahub.vw_person pab ON ((pab.id = t.assigned_by_seqid)))
     LEFT JOIN datahub.ticket_status s ON ((s.seqid = t.ticket_status_seqid)))
     LEFT JOIN datahub.ticket_sla sla ON ((sla.seqid = t.ticket_sla_seqid)))
     LEFT JOIN datahub.ticket_type tp ON ((tp.seqid = t.ticket_type_seqid)))
  WHERE (t.archive_dt IS NULL);

SELECT t.seqid AS ticket_id,
    t.summary,
    ta.seqid AS id,
    ta.common_id,
    ta.msg AS comment,
    ta.meta AS metadata,
    ta.search,
        CASE
            WHEN (t.resolution_ticket_activity_seqid = ta.seqid) THEN true
            ELSE false
        END AS is_resolution,
    ta.last_update_dt AS last_update_date,
    ta.record_create_dt AS create_date,
    ( SELECT pc.data
           FROM datahub.vw_person pc
          WHERE (pc.id = ta.creator_seqid)) AS creator,
    ( SELECT jsonb_agg(jsonb_build_object('id', att.seqid, 'uri', att.uri, 'name', att.nm, 'description', COALESCE(att.dsc, ''::text), 'metadata', att.meta, 'create_date', att.record_create_dt, 'creator', ( SELECT p4.data
                   FROM datahub.vw_person p4
                  WHERE (p4.id = att.creator_seqid)), 'last_update_date', att.last_update_dt)) AS jsonb_agg
           FROM datahub.ticket_attachment att
          WHERE (att.ticket_activity_seqid = ta.seqid)) AS attachments,
    ( SELECT vw_ticket_pin.data
           FROM datahub.vw_ticket_pin
          WHERE (vw_ticket_pin.ticket_activity_id = ta.seqid)) AS pins
   FROM (datahub.ticket_activity ta
     LEFT JOIN datahub.ticket t ON ((t.seqid = ta.ticket_seqid)))
  WHERE ((ta.archive_dt IS NULL) AND (t.archive_dt IS NULL));

SELECT ta.seqid AS ticket_activity_id,
    ta.ticket_seqid AS ticket_id,
    jsonb_build_object('sources', COALESCE(( SELECT jsonb_agg(jsonb_build_object('id', d1.id, 'name', d1.name, 'description', d1.description, 'aliases', d1.aliases)) AS jsonb_agg
           FROM (datahub.ticket_pin p1
             LEFT JOIN datahub.vw_data_source_ref d1 ON ((d1.id = p1.datastore_seqid)))
          WHERE ((p1.ticket_activity_seqid = ta.seqid) AND (p1.datastore_seqid IS NOT NULL))), '[]'::jsonb), 'sets', COALESCE(( SELECT jsonb_agg(jsonb_build_object('id', d2.id, 'name', d2.name, 'description', d2.description, 'aliases', d2.aliases)) AS jsonb_agg
           FROM (datahub.ticket_pin p2
             LEFT JOIN datahub.vw_data_set_ref d2 ON ((d2.id = p2.datatable_seqid)))
          WHERE ((p2.ticket_activity_seqid = ta.seqid) AND (p2.datatable_seqid IS NOT NULL))), '[]'::jsonb), 'items', COALESCE(( SELECT jsonb_agg(jsonb_build_object('id', d3.id, 'name', d3.name, 'description', d3.description, 'aliases', d3.aliases)) AS jsonb_agg
           FROM (datahub.ticket_pin p3
             LEFT JOIN datahub.vw_data_item_ref d3 ON ((d3.id = p3.datafield_seqid)))
          WHERE ((p3.ticket_activity_seqid = ta.seqid) AND (p3.datafield_seqid IS NOT NULL))), '[]'::jsonb), 'queries', COALESCE(( SELECT jsonb_agg(jsonb_build_object('id', d4.seqid, 'name', d4.nm, 'description', COALESCE(d4.dsc, ''::text))) AS jsonb_agg
           FROM (datahub.ticket_pin p4
             LEFT JOIN datahub.query d4 ON ((d4.seqid = p4.query_seqid)))
          WHERE ((p4.ticket_activity_seqid = ta.seqid) AND (d4.archive_dt IS NULL) AND (p4.query_seqid IS NOT NULL))), '[]'::jsonb)) AS data
   FROM datahub.ticket_activity ta
  WHERE (ta.archive_dt IS NULL);

SELECT t.id,
    ((((row_to_json(t.*))::jsonb - 'search'::text) - 'comments'::text) - 'linked_data'::text) AS ticket,
    t.search,
    NULL::jsonb AS comment,
    t.summary AS fuzzy_search,
    'ticket'::text AS type,
    t.create_date,
    (t.sla ->> 'id'::text) AS ticket_sla,
    (t.status ->> 'id'::text) AS ticket_status,
    (t.type ->> 'id'::text) AS ticket_type,
    (t.creator ->> 'username'::text) AS creator,
    (t.creator ->> 'display'::text) AS creator_name,
    (t.assignee ->> 'username'::text) AS assignee,
    (t.assignee ->> 'display'::text) AS assignee_name
   FROM datahub.vw_ticket t
UNION
 SELECT ta.common_id AS id,
    ((((row_to_json(t2.*))::jsonb - 'search'::text) - 'comments'::text) - 'linked_data'::text) AS ticket,
    ta.search,
    ((((((((row_to_json(ta.*))::jsonb - 'search'::text) - 'common_id'::text) - 'pins'::text) - 'attachments'::text) - 'ticket_id'::text) - 'summary'::text) || jsonb_build_object('comment_id', (string_to_array(ta.common_id, '-'::text))[1])) AS comment,
    ta.comment AS fuzzy_search,
    'comment'::text AS type,
    ta.create_date,
    (t2.sla ->> 'id'::text) AS ticket_sla,
    (t2.status ->> 'id'::text) AS ticket_status,
    (t2.type ->> 'id'::text) AS ticket_type,
    (ta.creator ->> 'username'::text) AS creator,
    (ta.creator ->> 'display'::text) AS creator_name,
    NULL::text AS assignee,
    NULL::text AS assignee_name
   FROM (datahub.vw_ticket_activity ta
     LEFT JOIN datahub.vw_ticket t2 ON ((t2.id = ta.ticket_id)));

metadata.view_source:
SELECT g.seqid AS id,
    g.nm AS name,
    COALESCE(g.dsc, ''::text) AS description,
    g.meta AS metadata,
    g.protected,
    g.record_create_dt AS create_date,
    ( SELECT jsonb_agg(DISTINCT jsonb_build_object('id', ug.seqid, 'name', ug.nm, 'description', COALESCE(ug.dsc, ''::text), 'metadata', ug.meta, 'protected', ug.protected, 'create_date', ug.record_create_dt)) AS jsonb_agg
           FROM (datahub.user_group ug
             LEFT JOIN datahub.group_member gm ON ((gm.user_subgroup_seqid = ug.seqid)))
          WHERE (gm.user_group_seqid = g.seqid)) AS member_groups,
    ( SELECT jsonb_agg(DISTINCT jsonb_build_object('id', ug2.seqid, 'name', ug2.nm, 'description', COALESCE(ug2.dsc, ''::text), 'metadata', ug2.meta, 'protected', ug2.protected, 'create_date', ug2.record_create_dt)) AS jsonb_agg
           FROM (datahub.user_group ug2
             LEFT JOIN datahub.group_member gm2 ON ((gm2.user_group_seqid = ug2.seqid)))
          WHERE (gm2.user_subgroup_seqid = g.seqid)) AS group_members,
    ( SELECT jsonb_agg(DISTINCT jsonb_build_object('id', ur.seqid, 'name', ur.nm, 'description', COALESCE(ur.dsc, ''::text), 'metadata', ur.meta, 'protected', ur.protected, 'create_date', ur.record_create_dt)) AS jsonb_agg
           FROM (datahub.user_role ur
             LEFT JOIN datahub.user_role_assignment ura ON ((ura.user_role_seqid = ur.seqid)))
          WHERE (ura.user_group_seqid = g.seqid)) AS assigned_roles,
    ( SELECT jsonb_agg(DISTINCT jsonb_build_object('id', l.seqid, 'username', l.username, 'description', COALESCE(l.dsc, ''::text), 'enabled', l.enabled, 'ldap', l.ldap_id, 'person', ( SELECT p.data
                   FROM datahub.vw_person p
                  WHERE (p.login_id = l.seqid)), 'create_date', l.record_create_dt)) AS jsonb_agg
           FROM (datahub.login l
             LEFT JOIN datahub.group_member gm3 ON ((gm3.login_seqid = l.seqid)))
          WHERE ((gm3.user_group_seqid = g.seqid) AND (l.archive_dt IS NULL))) AS users,
    ( SELECT jsonb_agg(DISTINCT jsonb_build_object('id', srr.seqid, 'name',
                CASE
                    WHEN (ra.force = 'd'::bpchar) THEN ('deny:'::text || srr.nm)
                    WHEN (ra.force = 'a'::bpchar) THEN ('allow:'::text || srr.nm)
                    ELSE srr.nm
                END, 'description', COALESCE(srr.dsc, ''::text), 'resource', jsonb_build_object('id', sr.seqid, 'name', sr.nm, 'description', COALESCE(sr.dsc, ''::text), 'create_date', sr.record_create_dt), 'create_date', srr.record_create_dt, 'assignment', jsonb_build_object('id', ra.seqid, 'create_date', ra.record_create_dt))) AS jsonb_agg
           FROM ((datahub.right_assign ra
             LEFT JOIN datahub.system_resource_right srr ON ((ra.right_seqid = srr.seqid)))
             LEFT JOIN datahub.system_resource sr ON ((sr.seqid = srr.system_resource_seqid)))
          WHERE (ra.group_seqid = g.seqid)) AS assigned_rights,
    (( SELECT DISTINCT jsonb_agg(DISTINCT y.x) AS jsonb_agg
           FROM ( SELECT jsonb_agg(DISTINCT jsonb_build_object('id', p.seqid, 'name', p.nm, 'description', COALESCE(p.dsc, ''::text), 'create_date', p.record_create_dt, 'assignment', json_build_object('id', up.seqid, 'create_date', up.record_create_dt, 'inherited',
                        CASE
                            WHEN (up.user_group_seqid IS NOT NULL) THEN false
                            ELSE true
                        END, 'inherited_from',
                        CASE
                            WHEN (up.user_group_seqid IS NOT NULL) THEN '[]'::jsonb
                            WHEN (up.user_role_seqid IN ( SELECT ura2x.user_role_seqid
                               FROM datahub.user_role_assignment ura2x
                              WHERE (ura2x.user_group_seqid = g.seqid))) THEN ( SELECT jsonb_agg(DISTINCT ur3x.nm) AS jsonb_agg
                               FROM (datahub.user_role ur3x
                                 LEFT JOIN datahub.user_role_assignment ura3x ON ((ur3x.seqid = ura3x.user_role_seqid)))
                              WHERE (ura3x.user_group_seqid = g.seqid))
                            ELSE '[]'::jsonb
                        END))) AS x
                   FROM (datahub.profile p
                     LEFT JOIN datahub.user_profile up ON ((up.profile_seqid = p.seqid)))
                  WHERE ((p.archive_dt IS NULL) AND ((up.user_group_seqid = g.seqid) OR (up.user_role_seqid IN ( SELECT ura2.user_role_seqid
                           FROM datahub.user_role_assignment ura2
                          WHERE (ura2.user_group_seqid = g.seqid)))))
                UNION
                 SELECT
                        CASE
                            WHEN (g.seqid IN ( SELECT ura3.user_group_seqid
                               FROM datahub.user_role_assignment ura3
                              WHERE ((ura3.user_role_seqid = 'datahub_admin'::text) AND (ura3.user_group_seqid IS NOT NULL)))) THEN jsonb_agg(DISTINCT jsonb_build_object('id', p2.seqid, 'name', p2.nm, 'description', COALESCE(p2.dsc, ''::text), 'create_date', p2.record_create_dt, 'assignment', jsonb_build_object('inherited', true, 'inherited_from', '["datahub_admin"]'::jsonb)))
                            ELSE NULL::jsonb
                        END AS x
                   FROM datahub.profile p2
                  WHERE (p2.archive_dt IS NULL)) y))[0] AS associated_profiles,
    ( SELECT jsonb_agg(DISTINCT jsonb_build_object('map_id', lm.seqid, 'dn', lm.dn, 'metadata', lm.meta, 'create_date', lm.record_create_dt)) AS jsonb_agg
           FROM datahub.ldap_map lm
          WHERE (lm.group_seqid = g.seqid)) AS ldap_mappings
   FROM datahub.user_group g
  ORDER BY g.nm, g.record_create_dt DESC;

SELECT r.seqid AS id,
    r.nm AS name,
    COALESCE(r.dsc, ''::text) AS description,
    r.meta AS metadata,
    r.protected,
    r.record_create_dt AS create_date,
    ( SELECT jsonb_agg(DISTINCT jsonb_build_object('id', l.seqid, 'username', l.username, 'description', COALESCE(l.dsc, ''::text), 'enabled', l.enabled, 'ldap', l.ldap_id, 'person', ( SELECT p.data
                   FROM datahub.vw_person p
                  WHERE (p.login_id = l.seqid)), 'create_date', ura.record_create_dt)) AS jsonb_agg
           FROM (datahub.login l
             LEFT JOIN datahub.user_role_assignment ura ON ((ura.login_seqid = l.seqid)))
          WHERE ((ura.user_role_seqid = r.seqid) AND (l.archive_dt IS NULL))) AS assigned_users,
    ( SELECT jsonb_agg(DISTINCT jsonb_build_object('map_id', lm.seqid, 'dn', lm.dn, 'metadata', lm.meta, 'create_date', lm.record_create_dt)) AS jsonb_agg
           FROM datahub.ldap_map lm
          WHERE (lm.role_seqid = r.seqid)) AS ldap_mappings,
    ( SELECT jsonb_agg(DISTINCT jsonb_build_object('id', ug.seqid, 'name', ug.nm, 'description', COALESCE(ug.dsc, ''::text), 'metadata', ug.meta, 'protected', ug.protected, 'create_date', ug.record_create_dt, 'assignment', jsonb_build_object('id', ura2.seqid, 'create_date', ura2.record_create_dt))) AS jsonb_agg
           FROM (datahub.user_role_assignment ura2
             LEFT JOIN datahub.user_group ug ON ((ug.seqid = ura2.user_group_seqid)))
          WHERE ((ura2.user_role_seqid = r.seqid) AND (ug.seqid IS NOT NULL))) AS assigned_groups,
    ( SELECT jsonb_agg(DISTINCT jsonb_build_object('id', srr.seqid, 'name',
                CASE
                    WHEN (ra.force = 'd'::bpchar) THEN ('deny:'::text || srr.nm)
                    WHEN (ra.force = 'a'::bpchar) THEN ('allow:'::text || srr.nm)
                    ELSE srr.nm
                END, 'description', COALESCE(srr.dsc, ''::text), 'resource', jsonb_build_object('id', sr.seqid, 'name', sr.nm, 'description', COALESCE(sr.dsc, ''::text), 'create_date', sr.record_create_dt), 'create_date', srr.record_create_dt, 'assignment', jsonb_build_object('id', ra.seqid, 'create_date', ra.record_create_dt))) AS jsonb_agg
           FROM ((datahub.right_assign ra
             LEFT JOIN datahub.system_resource_right srr ON ((ra.right_seqid = srr.seqid)))
             LEFT JOIN datahub.system_resource sr ON ((sr.seqid = srr.system_resource_seqid)))
          WHERE (ra.user_role_seqid = r.seqid)) AS assigned_rights,
    (( SELECT jsonb_agg(DISTINCT y.x) AS jsonb_agg
           FROM ( SELECT jsonb_agg(DISTINCT jsonb_build_object('id', p.seqid, 'name', p.nm, 'description', COALESCE(p.dsc, ''::text), 'create_date', p.record_create_dt, 'assignment', jsonb_build_object('inherited',
                        CASE
                            WHEN (up.user_role_seqid IS NOT NULL) THEN false
                            ELSE true
                        END, 'inherited_from',
                        CASE
                            WHEN (up.user_role_seqid IS NOT NULL) THEN '[]'::jsonb
                            ELSE ( SELECT jsonb_agg(DISTINCT dug.nm) AS jsonb_agg
                               FROM ((datahub.user_group dug
                                 LEFT JOIN datahub.user_role_assignment dura ON ((dura.user_group_seqid = dug.seqid)))
                                 LEFT JOIN datahub.user_profile dup ON ((dup.user_group_seqid = dug.seqid)))
                              WHERE ((dup.profile_seqid = p.seqid) AND (dura.user_role_seqid = r.seqid)))
                        END))) AS x
                   FROM (datahub.profile p
                     LEFT JOIN datahub.user_profile up ON ((up.profile_seqid = p.seqid)))
                  WHERE ((up.user_role_seqid = r.seqid) AND (p.archive_dt IS NULL))
                UNION
                 SELECT
                        CASE
                            WHEN (r.seqid = 'datahub_admin'::text) THEN jsonb_agg(DISTINCT jsonb_build_object('id', p2.seqid, 'name', p2.nm, 'description', COALESCE(p2.dsc, ''::text), 'create_date', p2.record_create_dt, 'assignment', jsonb_build_object('inherited', true, 'inherited_from', '["datahub_admin"]'::jsonb)))
                            ELSE NULL::jsonb
                        END AS x
                   FROM datahub.profile p2
                  WHERE (p2.archive_dt IS NULL)) y))[0] AS associated_profiles
   FROM datahub.user_role r
  ORDER BY r.nm;
